WEBVTT

00:03.728 --> 00:06.192
I haven't won any cooking contests,...

00:07.936 --> 00:11.379
...no ribbons for pies or awards for casseroles.

00:13.511 --> 00:15.579
Never been one for all that attention.

00:17.767 --> 00:20.142
If all my years in the kitchen have taught me anything,...

00:20.641 --> 00:24.551
...it's that when the right ingredients come together, it's magic.

00:27.003 --> 00:30.440
There's something about how each one brings its own special quality,...

00:30.519 --> 00:32.366
...its own piece of the puzzle.

00:37.775 --> 00:41.479
So, after all this time and all these years, you may ask,

00:42.182 --> 00:43.459
"Is it still worth it?"

00:45.513 --> 00:49.308
Well, if all my years in this family have taught me anything,...

00:50.688 --> 00:55.316
...is that when the right ingredients come together, it's magic.

00:57.517 --> 00:59.585
Publix: Where shopping is a pleasure.

